name: Cerebrum DAO
description: A community-driven translational research funding engine for brain health and accelerating solutions and cures to neurodegeneration. Cerebrum DAO members will take decisions on allocating funds to researchers & scientists specialized in the field of brain health and longevity with the aim to accelerate solutions for neurogenerative diseases. The DAO will also be responsible for take key decisions in continuously enhancing and developing the Cerebrum community to strengthen the bound between everyone in the community and drive results.
